INITIALIZARE PROIECT:

vezi: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tgR-vBuLd0Y

1. se va creea un template de proiect cu Spring Initializr:
 https://start.spring.io/

2. se inporta dependintele:
- Spring Boot Devtools;
- Spring Web;
- MySqL Driver;
- Spring Data JPA;

3. se genereaza template-ul;
4. se dezarhiveaza template-ul si se deschide in intellij;
- pasii de mai sus se pot face si direct in intellij cu SpringInitializr;
5.se configureaza in folderul resources in fisierul application.properties urmatoarele credentiale:

spring.datasource.url=jdbc:mysql://localhost:3306/bugtracker
spring.datasource.username=root
spring.datasource.password=root
spring.jpa.hibernate.ddl-auto=update
spring.jpa.show-sql=true
spring.jpa.database-platform=org.hibernate.dialect.MySQL8Dialect



INITIALIZARE ANGULAR - frontend framework:

1. se instaleaza node js - JavaScript runtime - v12.16.2 LTS (recommended for most users); - https://angular.io/guide/setup-local
2. Pasi:
- Step 1: Install the Angular CLI :  
npm install -g @angular/cli (in cmd)
- Step 2: Create a workspace and initial application
ng new my-app (in cmd)
- Step 3: Run the application
cd my-app
ng serve --open

Obligatoriu este Step1;






